Klasse MDocletEnvironment

java.lang.Object
org.jdrupes.mdoclet.internal.tool.DocEnvImpl
org.jdrupes.mdoclet.MDocletEnvironment
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
DocletEnvironment
public class MDocletEnvironment extends DocEnvImpl implements DocletEnvironment
Wraps the DocEnvImpl passed to the doclet for the sole purpose of inserting a wrapper for the doctrees access.
